{"tid":1469863,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"禁制令禁止機場指定範圍外示威但可在示威區內示威","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:46:57.000Z","uid":80373,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"68ea9a631806a0c16d19a3db7cde15171825fab4","tid":1469863,"uid":80373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"香港電台-港聞 <br />\n2019年8月14日 上午11:11<br />\n香港國際機場連日來有市民集會活動，機管局昨日入稟高等法院申請禁制令，並已取得該命令，禁止任何人在機場指定範圍以外包括禁區內，進行任何示威活動，但仍容許市民在和平合法的方式下，在示威專區內進行示威或集會。<br />\n<br />\n原告人為機管局，被告為非法或蓄意妨礙機場正常運作的人士。"},{"pid":"9a7139d08a078b987e89fd4ba2d3977992a55ebf","tid":1469863,"uid":80373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"1561221cbdc326d6d650424803ff354ada175149","tid":1469863,"uid":80373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"ac8d2d0e922796175d5f77c3464875baebafb1f0","tid":1469863,"uid":80373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"4f910b6fea0f4ea53488a3e28bc42c1e3aa523e0","tid":1469863,"uid":80373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"a94f3424443216c48de